{"title":"如何搭建hexo博客","uid":"14fa4b70da3229345c8f7ebad061c81c","slug":"如何搭建hexo博客","date":"2022-12-12T00:13:58.000Z","updated":"2022-12-13T03:00:00.388Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/如何搭建hexo博客.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ba98dc3c31c891a9d69ccbf45b07a107_r.jpg","content":"<p>经过重重困难，这个网站算是搭建好了<br>怎么样建一个像本站一样的博客站点<br>这篇文章将会很好的指引你<br>我会把我遇到的问题，以及解决问题的步骤和顺序写出来<br>后期会不断更新，有什么问题可以联系我<br>如果自己实在实在搞不定，给我发邮箱，我会抽空帮你一下<br>按照这个教程千万不要跳步，要不然很麻烦</p>\n<h3 id=\"软件准备\"><a href=\"#软件准备\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"软件准备\"></a>软件准备</h3><p>首先要下载的就是<a href=\"https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/download/\">node.js</a><br>然后还有很重要很重要的<a href=\"https://git-scm.com/downloads\">Git</a><br>因为我们这里文章编辑使用的是markdown语言<br>为此我们要下载一个<a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/Download\">Visual Studio Code</a>进行编辑，当然也可以下载Typora，两款软件都很不错<br>VS Code是一个非常好的编辑器，就算不写Markdown也可以用来写别的程序<br>Typora就是专注于Markdown了，我最推荐大家有条件就支持正版：89元终生使用<a href=\"https://www.typoraio.cn/\">Typora官方下载</a><br>没有条件也想用Typora没关系，我把我朋友Kevin找到的可靠破解版薅过来了<a href=\"https://kevinwu06.lanzout.com/iXkq30icv1ha\">Typora破解版</a><br>安装好之后我们在CMD输入一下命令，检查是否安装成功</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">node -v\nnpm -v(node附带的)\ngit -v</code></pre>\n<p>如果这里都能输出对应的版本号，没有报错的话就是正常了，可以进行到下一步，如果报错了，就需要重装一下。</p>\n<h3 id=\"创建仓库\"><a href=\"#创建仓库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建仓库\"></a>创建仓库</h3><p>登录<a href=\"https://github.com/\">Github</a><br><img src=\"https://i.328888.xyz/2022/12/12/y83NU.png\" alt=\"avatar\"><br>如果已经有账号就点击“Sign in”<br>如果没有账号就点击“Sign up”，按照他的步骤输入邮箱、账号、密码注册新账号<br>登录成功之后进入到主界面<br>右上角在头像的左边有一个加号，点击加号<br>在下拉菜单里面点击“New organization”</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.328888.xyz/2022/12/13/yr0IQ.png\" alt=\"avatar\"><br>在新页面点击最左边的“Free”下面的“Create a free organization”，因为免费的已经够用了。</p>\n<p>在新的页面填入你的站名，比如我的就是”timewaster43”<br>然后填上一个邮箱，“This organization belongs to:”选择“My personal account”<br>完成人机测试，勾选同意协议，点击”Next“就可以了</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img1.imgtp.com/2022/12/13/EYau9W7e.jpg\" alt=\"avatar\"><br>在这个界面，如果你是多人编辑，那就填入队友的名字，如果像我一样是一个人就点击下面蓝色的”Skip this step“来跳过这个步骤</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img1.imgtp.com/2022/12/13/YywHMpFL.jpg\" alt=\"avatar\"><br>在这个界面随便选一下，提交就可以了，没有什么重要的<br>做完这里能成功进入组织管理界面就是组织创建成功了<br>接着，再点击右上角的加号，点击“New repository”新建仓库<br><img src=\"https://img1.imgtp.com/2022/12/13/RRHIREQJ.jpg\" alt=\"avatar\"><br>这里的owner选择刚刚新建的那个组织的名字，“Repository name”填“owner名.github.io”<br>比如我在这里的就是“timewasterxlz.github.io”<br>下面这两个选项一定要选“Public”!!!<br>勾选“Add a README file”</p>\n<p>最后的成果应该是这样：<br><img src=\"https://img1.imgtp.com/2022/12/13/KcpMV9Ne.jpg\" alt=\"avatar\"><br>如果是这样，那就设置成功了，可以提交了</p>\n<h3 id=\"生成SSH-Keys\"><a href=\"#生成SSH-Keys\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"生成SSH Keys\"></a>生成SSH Keys</h3>","feature":"ture","text":"经过重重困难，这个网站算是搭建好了怎么样建一个像本站一样的博客站点这篇文章将会很好的指引你我会把我遇到的问题，以及解决问题的步骤和顺序写出来后期会不断更新，有什么问题可以联系我如果自己实在实在搞不定，给我发邮箱，我会抽空帮你一下按照这个教程千万不要跳步，要不然很麻烦 软件准备首先...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"技术","slug":"技术","count":2,"path":"api/tags/技术.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">软件准备</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\">创建仓库</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90SSH-Keys\"><span class=\"toc-text\">生成SSH Keys</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"timewaster","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/static/img/pic.png","link":"/","description":"一个天天摆烂的人","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/timewaster43","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/433838433?spm_id_from=333.1007.0.0"},"twitter":{"icon":"/svg/twitter.svg","link":"https://twitter.com/Benjami88527920"},"mail":{"icon":"/svg/mail.svg","link":"mailto:timewasterpro@163.com"},"zhihu":{"icon":"/svg/zh.svg","link":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/jun-yuan-qian-wen"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"关于你睡觉的事实","uid":"cf05c9ec76d210c68651d021e15ebf2b","slug":"关于你睡觉的事实","date":"2022-12-11T01:33:20.000Z","updated":"2022-12-11T16:48:43.846Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/关于你睡觉的事实.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://images7.alphacoders.com/100/1002684.jpg","text":"前言不知道各位读者最近的睡眠状况怎么样，有没有做梦，说梦话什么的。其实这个话题在我们生活中真的很常见，大家见面可能都会聊。我本人在这方面其实一直有一些问题，就是我会说梦话，也会梦游，所以在上周这个课题研究的时候做了一些research，也跟大家分享一下。 做梦为什么人在睡觉的时候...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.3k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"无话不聊","slug":"无话不聊","count":1,"path":"api/tags/无话不聊.json"}],"author":{"name":"timewaster","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/static/img/pic.png","link":"/","description":"一个天天摆烂的人","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/timewaster43","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/433838433?spm_id_from=333.1007.0.0"},"twitter":{"icon":"/svg/twitter.svg","link":"https://twitter.com/Benjami88527920"},"mail":{"icon":"/svg/mail.svg","link":"mailto:timewasterpro@163.com"},"zhihu":{"icon":"/svg/zh.svg","link":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/jun-yuan-qian-wen"}}}},"feature":true}}